<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4701.3.4>
    bibo:endPage "290" ;
    bibo:issue "3" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2019-11-28" ;
    bibo:startPage "276" ;
    bibo:volume "4701" ;
    dc:creator "Kosterin, Oleg E." ;
    dc:date "2019" ;
    dc:title "Description of a female and variation of Microgomphus alani Kosterin, 2016 (Odonata: Gomphidae) in Cambodia, with a note on sexual dimorphism in Microgomphus spp." ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3558041>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3558043>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3558049>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3558051>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3558045>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3558053>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3558047> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3558041>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Male (a, d–e) and female (b–c) specimens of Microgomphus alani in live colours from the Phnom Kulen Mountains, Siem Reap Province (a–c) and Mondulkiri Province (d–e) of Cambodia, 11 vi 2018 (c), 17 vi 2018 (a), 30 vi 2018 (b) and 26 vi 2018 (d–e). Not to scale" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3558041/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3558043>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Dry male (a, d–e) and female (b–c, f) specimens of Microgomphus alani from the Phnom Kulen Mountains, Siem Reap Province (a–c) and Mondulkiri Province (d–f) of Cambodia, collected on 3 viii 2016 (f), 11 vi 2018 (c), 17 vi 2018 (a), 30 vi 2018 (b) and 26 vi 2018 (d–e)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3558043/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3558049>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Frontal view of head (left) and occiput (right) of female specimens of Microgomphus alani collected on 3 viii 2016 in Mondulkiri Province (a; the same specimen as in Fig. 2f) and in the Phnom Kulen Mts on 11 vi 2018 (b, the same specimen as in Figs 1c, 2c) and 30 vi 2018 (c, the same specimen as in Figs 1b, 2b). Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3558049/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3558051>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Details of female specimens of Microgomphus alani collected in Mondulkiri Province on 3 viii 2016 (c,e; the same specimen as in Fig. 2f) and in the Phnom Kulen Mts on 11 vi 2018 (a,f; the same specimen as in Fig. 1c and Fig 2c) and on 30 vi 2018 (b,d,g; the same specimen as in Figs 1b, 2b): a–b—head and thorax, lateral view; c–d—pterothorax, dorsal view; e–g—vulvar lamina, ventral view. Scale bars, from top to bottom, 4 mm, 2 mm and 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3558051/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3558045>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Details of male specimens of Microgomphus alani collected on 26 vi 2018 in Mondulkiri Province (a–d; the same specimen as in Fig. 2d) and on 17 vi 2018 in the Phnom Kulen Mts (a–h, the same specimen as in Fig. 1a and Fig 2a): a,e—head and thorax, lateral view; b,f—pterothorax, dorsal view; c,g—head, frontal (c) and dorsofrontal (g) view; d,h—secondary genitalia, lateral view. Scale bars. from top to bottom, 4 mm, 2 mm, 2 mm and 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3558045/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3558053>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Hind legs of Microgomphus alani, a—male from Mondulkiri Province, 13 vi 2014; b—female from Modulkiri Province, 3 viii 2016; c—female from Phnom Kulen Mts, 30 vi 2018. Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3558053/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3558047>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Anal appendages, in dorsal (left) and lateral (right) view, of mature males of Microgomphus alani, collected on 26 vi 2018 in Mondulkiri Province (a–b, respectively corresponding to the specimens in Fig. 2d and Fig. 2e) and on 17 vi 2018 in the Phnom Kulen Mts (c, correspond to Fig. 1a and Fig 2a). Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3558047/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

